{"title":"病床小记——赠医护同志们","authors":["宋文"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":7,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"病床小记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——赠医护同志们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宋文"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请别提起烽火连天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——身上那些弹洞伤眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沸腾的血染画着祖国江山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，我们在这儿重又见面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您们依然穿着素白长衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们固有的亲密无间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把生命活力点点滴滴地输入血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慈母般地关怀体贴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽早的让我们再上前线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！您们象宇宙里的繁星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"普照着我们的心田。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}